edgeR DE

pData<-pData[match(colnames(exprs), pData$DLPFC_RNA_Sequencing_Sample_ID ), ]

group<-as.factor(na.omit(pData$treatmentType[-grep("_08", pData$DLPFC_RNA_Sequencing_Sample_ID)]))
c <- DGEList(counts = exprs[,-c(grep("_08", colnames(exprs)), ncol(exprs))], genes = exprs$gene, group = group) # tab$TSS_Class=="TRUE" 53
design <- model.matrix(~0+group)
c <- calcNormFactors(c, method = "TMM")
c <- estimateGLMTrendedDisp(c,design)
c <- estimateGLMTagwiseDisp(c, design)
fit <- glmFit(c, design)
c <- estimateCommonDisp(c)
c <- estimateTagwiseDisp(c)
norm_counts.table <- t(t(c$pseudo.counts)*(c$samples$norm.factors))

specific DE genes

m<-rep(0,ncol(design))
aa<-grep("placebo", colnames(design))
vv<-grep("clozapine", colnames(design))
m[aa]<- -1/length(aa) ### cont
m[vv]<- 1/length(vv) ## exp
lrt <- glmLRT(fit, contrast = m)
names<-unlist(strsplit(gsub('1*group', '', lrt$comparison, fixed = T), split = " ", fixed = T))
topTags(lrt, n=nrow(lrt$table))$table -> final1
final1[final1$PValue < 0.05, ] -> clozapine

cloz_genes_all <- clozapine$genes
halo_genes_all <- haloperidol$genes

halo_genes_hs <- haloperidol$genes[-grep("ENSMMU", haloperidol$genes)]

load SC cao data

load("/home/pkharchenko/konstantin/schizo/revision/validation/.RData")
de_genes<-cao$estimatePerCellTypeDE(max.cell.count = 50, name='deFixed', resampling.method='bootstrap', max.resamplings=29)
## DE method DESeq2.Wald is used

get overlapping genes

overlap_cloz_all_num<-numeric()
overlap_halo_all_num<-numeric()
num_of_de_genes<-numeric()
for(i in 1:length(de_genes)){
  genes_a <- rownames(de_genes[[i]]$res[de_genes[[i]]$res$pvalue < 0.05, ])
  overlap_cloz_all <- intersect(genes_a, cloz_genes_all)
  overlap_halo_all <- intersect(genes_a, halo_genes_all)
  overlap_cloz_all_num <- c(overlap_cloz_all_num, length(overlap_cloz_all))
  overlap_halo_all_num <- c(overlap_halo_all_num, length(overlap_halo_all))
  num_of_de_genes <- c(num_of_de_genes, length(genes_a))
}
my.df <- data.frame(de=num_of_de_genes, cloz=overlap_cloz_all_num, halo=overlap_halo_all_num)

test overlaps significance

sim_pval_list<-numeric()
hyper_pval_list<-numeric()
hyper_pval_list_halo<-numeric()
for(i in 1:length(de_genes)){
  # sc
  sets<-list(rownames(de_genes[[i]]$res[de_genes[[i]]$res$pvalue < 0.05, ]), cloz_genes_hs)
  lengths(sets)
  observed <- length(purrr::reduce(sets, intersect))
  all_genes <-  rownames(de_genes[[i]]$res)
  hyper_pval <- phyper(
    q=observed, m=length(sets[[1]]),
    n=length(all_genes) - length(sets[[1]]),
    k=length(sets[[2]]), lower.tail=FALSE
  )
  hyper_pval_list <- c(hyper_pval_list, hyper_pval)
  sets<-list(rownames(de_genes[[i]]$res[de_genes[[i]]$res$pvalue < 0.05, ]), halo_genes_hs)
  lengths(sets)
  observed <- length(purrr::reduce(sets, intersect))
  all_genes <-  rownames(de_genes[[i]]$res)
  hyper_pval <- phyper(
    q=observed, m=length(sets[[1]]),
    n=length(all_genes) - length(sets[[1]]),
    k=length(sets[[2]]), lower.tail=FALSE
  )
  hyper_pval_list_halo <- c(hyper_pval_list_halo, hyper_pval)
}

plot barplot

library(RColorBrewer)
cols<-brewer.pal(8, "Set3")[-2]

par(mai=c(3, .8, .1, .1), oma=c(1,1,1,1))

text(x = bp[2,],y =  num_of_de_genes, labels = paste("p.val ", round(hyper_pval_list, 2),"; ", round(hyper_pval_list_halo, 2), sep=""), srt=90, cex=0.7)
legend("topleft", bty="n", pch=15, col=cols[1:3], legend = c("DE genes", "overlap to clozapine", "overlap to haloperidol" ))
